                  <additions>
                    <list>
                      <item xml:id="a01">
                      <desc type="Asmat">
                      <locus target="#iv(erso) #1r"/> Asmat prayer for help in learning
                      </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="e01">
                      <desc>
                      <locus target="#ir(ecto) #1v #151r #151v"/> Blank except for scrawls and pen trials
                      </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="a02">
                      <desc>
                      <locus target="#117r"/> #bottom three lines, continued on <locus target="#136r"/>, bottom five lines,:
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይቤሉ፡ አበዊነ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ እለ፡ አርአዮሙ፡ ኅቡአተ፡ ምሥጢራቲሁ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አምላኮሙ፡ ወከመዝ፡ ውእቱ፡ ፍሬሁ፡ ለ፩፡ መዝሙረ፡ ዳዊት፡ ፺፼ወ፷፻፡ ወዘንተሰ፡ እለ፡
                      ይዜ <locus target="#136"/> ምሩ፡ በአንብዕ፡ ወበፈሪሃ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወበሠናይ፡ መልእክት፡ ዘይጼሊ፡ በቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ነጐርጓር፡ ፳፻፼፲፻፡ በምሥራቅ፡ ፳፻፼፲፻፡ በምዕራብ፡ በሰሜን፡ ወበደቡብ፡ ከማሁ፡ ይከውን፡ ፍሬሁ፡ ይቤሉ። ወካዕበ፡ ይቤሉ፡ አሐቲ፡ ሰጊድ፡ ፷፼፡ ፍሬሁ፡</foreign>
                      “Our holy fathers to whom God, their creator, revealed hidden mysteries, said, ‘the (spiritual) fruit of one psalm is 106,000.’”
                      “And those who sing with tears and the fear of God and with good intent and who pray in the church without complaining [will have spiritual fruit in the quantities of] 2,000 times 10,000 in the East, 2,000 times 10,000 in the West, and the same for North and South.
                      And also they said, ‘the fruit of one bow is 60,000.’”
                      </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="a03">
